sources.description:
*Unfallen* - During the Civil War in Tajikistan, Rustam and Suhrob's parents are blown up by a missile. Seven-year old twins are separated, years later they meet in a new war, where one is an American soldier and the other is Taliban.
2017 War Movie | Stars: Michael Madsen, James Hong, Stephen Chang
